Review control description: NBFCs shall communicate, not later than one month from the occurrence of any
change in:
(1) the names and residential addresses of the directors of the company;

Review control description: The issues shall be governed by the following instructions:
(1) The minimum subscription per investor shall be ₹20,000 (Rupees Twenty
thousand);

Review control description: (3) There shall be a limit of 200 subscribers for every financial year, for issuance of
NCDs with a maximum subscription of less than ₹1 crore, and such subscription
shall be fully secured;

Review control description: <image>
(4) It shall be earning profits for the last three years and its performance shall be
satisfactory;
